OL,3,CNo 10 criticises London theatre's
OL,4,C'divisive' plans for black-only nights
OL,6,FDowning Street has said plans to hold
OL,7,Fblack-only nights at a London theatre
OL,8,Fare "wrong and divisive".
OL,10,FSlave Play will be staged at the Noel
OL,11,FCoward Theatre this summer, and was
OL,12,Fset to have two performances aimed at
OL,13,Fan "all-black-identifying audience"
OL,14,Fthat is "free from the white gaze".
OL,16,FSince the intervention by No 10, the
OL,17,Fproducers of the play said they are
OL,18,F"carefully considering" the black-only
OL,19,Fnights.
