OL,6,FA statement from the producers to the
OL,7,FPA news agency said: "Our intent is to
OL,8,Fcelebrate the play with the widest
OL,9,Fpossible audience.
OL,11,F"We want to increase accessibility to
OL,12,Ftheatre for everyone.
OL,14,F"The Broadway production conceived
OL,15,FBlack Out nights and we are carefully
OL,16,Fconsidering how to incorporate this
OL,17,Fendeavour as part of two performances
OL,18,Fin our 13-week run.
