OL,6,F"Obviously, these reports are
OL,7,Fconcerning and further information is
OL,8,Fbeing sought.
OL,10,F"But clearly, restricting audiences on
OL,11,Fthe basis of race would be wrong and
OL,12,Fdivisive."
OL,14,FAsked if that was an implied threat
OL,15,Fabout withdrawing taxpayer support,
OL,16,Fthe spokesman said: "No, it is a
OL,17,Fstatement of principle that clearly
OL,18,Fthe arts should be inclusive.
