OL,11,Fnights, writer Jeremy O Harris wrote
OL,12,Fon X, formerly Twitter: "I don't have
OL,13,Fto imagine the roles were reversed in
OL,14,Fmy grandparents' lifetimes AND WORSE.
OL,16,F"I'm not even saying BLACKS ONLY I'm
OL,17,Fsaying I'm inviting black ppl first!
OL,18,FThey can bring their white friends or
OL,19,Flovers if they want. There's no colour
OL,20,Fbar. But one existed in the UK
OL,21,Frecently!"
