OL,6,FSlave Play tells a story of "race,
OL,7,Fidentity and sexuality" at the
OL,8,FMacGregor Plantation in the southern
OL,9,FUS during the early 21st century.
OL,11,FIt was nominated for a record 12 Tony
OL,12,FAwards after its hugely successful on
OL,13,FBroadway.
OL,15,FThe play stars Game of Thrones star
OL,16,FKit Harrington, and Denzel
OL,17,FWashington's daughter Olivia
OL,18,FWashington.
